				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/B%E1%BB%99i-ho%C3%A0ng/poem-Mz3APMDkhSRcMiueTZKtXw">Bội hoàng - 捕蝗</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/H%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-Xu-Ng%C3%B4n-th%E1%BA%A3o-c%C3%A1c-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-1xg3hi80FKcKoSCSEece2g">Hí đề Xu Ngôn thảo các tam thập nhị vận - 戲題樞言草閣三十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADp-B%E1%BA%B1ng/Huy%C3%AAn-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-cAnSa_xzcx7BR79C1ypBFw">Huyên thảo - 萱草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Th%E1%BA%ADp-B%E1%BA%B1ng/author-ewpTlof-SVjHfI-DvlAHOA">Vương Thập Bằng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Minh-nguy%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0-h%E1%BA%A1o-h%E1%BA%A1o/poem-bvnxS3cY7aBedngIDzLAog">Minh nguyệt hà hạo hạo - 明月何皎皎</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ph%C3%B9-du-2/poem-yYI1s1bl5ww29qnLt-_-gQ">Phù du 2 - 蜉蝣 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BA%A3o-tri%E1%BB%81u-Trung-Ho%C3%A0-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87n-t%E1%BB%A9-n%E1%BB%99i-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-chi%E1%BA%BFn-th%E1%BB%A7-t%E1%BA%A5u-ngh%E1%BB%8B-cung-k%C3%BD/poem-FlGm8Uvq1cyxmk9iiiFSiQ">Tảo triều Trung Hoà điện tứ nội, độc chiến thủ tấu nghị cung ký - 早朝中和殿賜入內侍讀戰守奏議恭記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/T%E1%BA%A7n-trung-ng%C3%A2m-k%E1%BB%B3-05-B%E1%BA%A5t-tr%C3%AD-s%C4%A9/poem-KrJPC57LWUez8WQKzHaIMQ">Tần trung ngâm kỳ 05 - Bất trí sĩ - 秦中吟其五－不致仕</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADch-bi%E1%BB%87t-h%C3%A0nh-t%E1%BB%91ng-L%C6%B0u-b%E1%BB%99c-x%E1%BA%A1-ph%C3%A1n-quan/poem-dW12UVYh-vPxg4IlKpEmEA">Tích biệt hành, tống Lưu bộc xạ phán quan - 惜別行送劉僕射判官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ph%C3%BA-L%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1t-c%E1%BA%A3nh-k%E1%BB%B3-6-Linh-Th%C3%A1i/poem-Y6cxMFq5zXo0K9M-XGtWIg">Vịnh Phú Lộc bát cảnh kỳ 6 - Linh Thái - 詠富祿八景其六－靈蔡</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-th%E1%BB%8B-gia-nhi/poem-_idfLH-CKR1qIP7JofaBPA">Xuân nhật thị gia nhi - 春日示家兒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br></div>	</div>
